snippet.title: Htc Vive - Roomscale Coaster Gameplay
snippet.description:
Using alot of room space , this game puts you on a platform rollercoaster while trying to collect orbs and dodge giant walls. Its a fast paced intense workout type of game. Are you good enough?

Roomscale coaster on steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/592330/

Thanks for watching everyone! 
Dont forget to subscribe.
